{
  "stem": "293.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the rumors came in that they were having a close part of city only for Jews to keep them under the supervision and protected them from the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's the reason they want to consolidate them in one part of city in city of Cracow, down in [INAUDIBLE], there's a suburb.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I personally didn't like the idea, but we said, let-- let's try to get the permission to, to do this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we apply.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Coincidentally, my family was not protected by the Jewish Federation because they were not essential worker over there, and we didn't get it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have to move from the city to any place we want east from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So because my brother-in-law, husband of my sister, Pauline, was from Sanok, they decide to go to Sanok.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I decide with Mila to go to Sanok, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then I got a bright idea, why should I move from Cracow?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was born here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't do anything wrong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I will go to the city hall and ask them for the permission to stay in Cracow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I went dressed beautifully with a Jewish armband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I went there and asked for the mayor of the city, Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Pavlo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They said Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Pavlo is not here, but his assistant is here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, I don't care.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I will talk to his assistant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what they bringing me to a-- to a beautiful office, and behind the desk is an SS officer sitting, a handsome guy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I couldn't believe it, my eye.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a friend of mine, who was-- from Vienna, who was instructor of Polish National Ski, Ski Team.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1939 in February was first federation international ski exercises in Zakopane in the mountains-- winter type of Olympics game.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
